{"tid":1276320,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[正名運動] 要得到關注，必須有個統一既名稱","createTime":"2019-07-02T02:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T15:33:45.000Z","uid":52658,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d97f3d37654d110822c52d378739abcdcd18eea2","tid":1276320,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:34:07.000Z","msg":"捷克有布拉格之春<br />\n東歐有東歐劇變<br />\n中東有阿拉伯之春<br />\n台灣有太陽花學運<br />\n美國有佔領華爾街<br />\n<br />\n但今次單野有無一個相關既名稱去稱呼今次示威？<br />\n由6月9號 一直到琴日既佔領立法會<br />\n西方世界係點樣稱呼呢件事？<br />\n唔好話西方世界 我地香港都無一個名比佢啦<br />\n反送中示威？反修例遊行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果d鬼佬要search 應該要打咩keywords 先<br />\n個人認為應該要做個名比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n令事件可以比更加多人知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de2ba4152da9b0f9877895a6a8ef97615e96b7b","tid":1276320,"uid":232923,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:35:03.000Z","msg":"獵鷹行動"},{"pid":"1947061d0dc38b5d5e18c281027c68485a5b6c96","tid":1276320,"uid":237628,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:38:09.000Z","msg":"血色六月"},{"pid":"67aebb9811334746c97e3134772f6d3ba85f6837","tid":1276320,"uid":237628,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:38:40.000Z","msg":"黑紫荊運動"},{"pid":"8c5e95ed6677001cc1d1185b3a1ac61e7cc352e1","tid":1276320,"uid":128869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:46:43.000Z","msg":"金鐘覺醒"},{"pid":"2eb828d6d81269a0fda06fb8757d67184b0c7143","tid":1276320,"uid":237628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b783795d03e6f30872a7b1ced6be402a4a7088d2","tid":1276320,"uid":237628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:08:44.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4d73a9e545db099e11941a57b47943bf9a786726","tid":1276320,"uid":237628,"like":0,"dislike":0,